data.title: Apple’s quiet AI era just got a very loud replacement
data.description: Apple has a new AI boss, a delayed Siri reboot, and edgy investors. Now, Gemini veteran Amar Subramanya must turn invisible AI into visible upside
data.keywords: Apple, Tim Cook, Apple Park, Apple Intelligence, Amar Subramanya, Google, John Giannandrea, Subramanya, generative AI, personal intelligence
